_sText:
Created for KSF's 2020 Fall surf mapping competition.

----------
Type: Linear
Difficulty: Tier 2
Length: 35-50s
Default maxvelocity
----------

Time from first work in hammer to map completion was about 3 weeks. Bulk of the time was spent on the ramps and displacements.

All models in the map including surf ramps, trees, tree roots, and crystals were created by me (anonymous6366 aka FriendlyChemist) in 3dsmax. Big thanks to TopHattwaffle for his tutorials on 3dsmax, they were hugely helpful when I was getting started out with 3dsmax.

CSGO port soon
